    <data key="d0">Assembly AI Scalable ML Inference Architecture</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vQgUkn3rAMY</data>
    <data key="d2">Handles millions of daily audio API requests. Implements custom predictive scaling for GPU tasks to optimize ECS container costs. Strictly enforces S3 lifecycle policies for SOC 2 security compliance.</data>
